WEBVTT

01:52.870 --> 01:55.039
The medicines prescribed for
His Majesty have had no effect.

01:55.039 --> 01:57.150
What should we do?

01:57.150 --> 01:58.950
I'm afraid this may cause chaos.

02:00.430 --> 02:01.920
Lord Zhang, Lord Li.

02:01.920 --> 02:03.430
How is His Majesty?

02:03.430 --> 02:04.590
Nothing serious,

02:05.480 --> 02:06.680
just a minor illness.

02:07.230 --> 02:09.190
But I heard from an imperial physician

02:09.190 --> 02:10.990
that His Majesty is gravely ill.

02:11.590 --> 02:12.840
If he doesn't recover soon,

02:12.840 --> 02:14.080
then... -How dare you!

02:14.080 --> 02:16.000
Who spouted such nonsense?

02:16.030 --> 02:18.470
I'll have his entire clan executed
for His Majesty.

02:18.470 --> 02:19.240
My lords,

02:20.030 --> 02:21.840
you are all
important ministers in the court,

02:21.840 --> 02:23.400
holding positions of great authority.

02:23.400 --> 02:25.660
How can you believe every rumor you hear?

02:26.150 --> 02:29.880
I was appointed Chief Grand Secretary
by the late emperor himself.

02:30.079 --> 02:31.870
If my words carry no weight with you,

02:31.870 --> 02:32.840
would you really

02:32.840 --> 02:35.470
place your trust in an imperial physician?

02:35.630 --> 02:36.590
Lord Li.

02:36.750 --> 02:39.750
We must severely punish those
who deceive the public.

02:39.750 --> 02:40.560
Yes.

02:41.030 --> 02:41.960
My lords,

02:42.280 --> 02:43.150
go back.

02:43.280 --> 02:45.410
Court will convene as usual tomorrow.

02:45.430 --> 02:47.280
If anyone dares neglect his duties,

02:47.280 --> 02:49.400
I will show no mercy.

02:50.030 --> 02:50.750
Yes.

02:50.750 --> 02:51.750
You may leave now.

02:54.190 --> 02:55.079
Your Majesty.

02:55.430 --> 02:56.840
What happened to you?

02:58.000 --> 02:59.800
Wake up and look at me.

03:01.870 --> 03:03.680
What happened to you?

03:10.030 --> 03:11.800
Wake up and look at me.

03:13.190 --> 03:15.000
The imperial physicians say
there's no hope for you—

03:15.000 --> 03:17.120
but how can that be?

03:17.520 --> 03:18.190
Liu Chu.

03:19.470 --> 03:20.470
Wake up.

03:23.190 --> 03:24.280
Look at me.

03:25.470 --> 03:27.030
I am Jiang Wanyu.

03:27.840 --> 03:29.590
Open your eyes.

03:33.590 --> 03:34.750
Liu Chu.

03:36.590 --> 03:37.720
Did I not decree that

03:37.800 --> 03:38.630
no one is to approach

03:38.630 --> 03:40.630
His Majesty without my order?

03:41.000 --> 03:41.910
But...

03:41.910 --> 03:43.190
Consort Ling is...

03:43.560 --> 03:44.630
And you still dare to make excuses?

03:44.630 --> 03:45.520
Get out.

03:45.520 --> 03:47.050
Give yourself forty slaps.

03:47.190 --> 03:48.000
Yes.

03:52.030 --> 03:52.870
Xie.

03:54.630 --> 03:55.960
Don't be too sad.

03:56.150 --> 03:57.750
The imperial physicians
are trying to find a way.

03:57.750 --> 04:00.000
But they all say there's no hope for him.

04:02.750 --> 04:04.470
You are with child.

04:04.560 --> 04:06.360
Be careful not to harm the fetus.

04:07.080 --> 04:07.960
Guards,

04:08.030 --> 04:09.280
escort Consort Ling back to her palace

04:09.280 --> 04:10.680
and take good care of her.

04:11.080 --> 04:11.960
Xie.

04:12.080 --> 04:12.560
I...

04:13.280 --> 04:15.010
You are His Majesty's consort,

04:15.080 --> 04:17.040
and you are carrying his child.

04:17.390 --> 04:18.630
At all times,

04:18.630 --> 04:20.630
you must put the imperial heir first.

04:20.630 --> 04:21.690
Do you understand?

04:21.870 --> 04:24.000
I want to stay with him a little longer.

04:28.950 --> 04:29.810
Your Highness.

04:31.720 --> 04:32.680
Your Highness.

04:33.159 --> 04:34.560
Let's go, Your Highness.

04:48.480 --> 04:50.000
This prescription is too strong.

04:50.000 --> 04:51.870
I suggest adding Scutellaria

04:51.870 --> 04:53.070
for it to take effect.

04:53.430 --> 04:54.360
No, no.

04:54.510 --> 04:56.270
Scutellaria is too strong.

04:56.560 --> 04:57.890
It may harm His Majesty.

04:57.950 --> 05:00.630
We should replace it with Forsythia.

05:00.750 --> 05:02.070
Dandelion can also detoxify.

05:02.070 --> 05:03.270
We might as well include it as well.

05:03.270 --> 05:04.630
I still think Scutellaria is better.

05:04.630 --> 05:05.480
My lords.

05:05.950 --> 05:07.000
If I may be blunt,

05:07.160 --> 05:08.680
while your prescriptions are sound,

05:08.680 --> 05:11.160
they may not be suitable for
His Majesty's current condition.

05:11.160 --> 05:12.190
Who are you

05:12.390 --> 05:14.000
to interfere here?

05:14.070 --> 05:15.510
How dare you question us?

05:16.070 --> 05:18.160
This is Han Yunling, who cured the plague

05:18.160 --> 05:19.290
in Huangpi Village.

05:19.600 --> 05:21.190
But it doesn't mean

05:21.190 --> 05:22.750
she can cure His Majesty.

05:22.950 --> 05:24.800
What this physician says is reasonable.

05:24.800 --> 05:27.270
But you've been arguing here
for so long without any result.

05:27.270 --> 05:29.190
If you are willing to hear me out,

05:29.240 --> 05:30.480
we may be able to find

05:30.480 --> 05:32.010
a more suitable treatment.

05:33.600 --> 05:35.270
We veteran imperial physicians

05:35.270 --> 05:36.830
have served His Majesty for years.

05:36.830 --> 05:37.800
Why should we

05:38.120 --> 05:40.070
listen to a mere girl like you?

05:40.070 --> 05:41.630
Medicine has no rank

05:41.630 --> 05:42.800
or gender.

05:42.800 --> 05:44.830
Everyone here is an esteemed physician.

05:44.830 --> 05:45.800
What's more,

05:45.920 --> 05:47.240
the poison in Huangpi Village

05:47.240 --> 05:48.680
that left everyone helpless

05:48.680 --> 05:50.870
was cured by Physician Han here.

05:51.680 --> 05:53.630
If none of you have a solution,

05:54.070 --> 05:55.390
why not let me try?

06:03.830 --> 06:04.830
Physician Han.

06:05.240 --> 06:06.430
These are His Majesty's

06:06.430 --> 06:09.040
full symptoms and treatment records.

06:09.040 --> 06:11.480
He first fell into a coma,

06:11.800 --> 06:15.070
followed by a persistent low-grade fever,

06:15.070 --> 06:18.070
and now he has widespread bruising.

06:19.600 --> 06:20.720
Could you please

06:20.720 --> 06:22.800
elaborate further on

06:23.070 --> 06:25.430
the medications His Majesty has taken
and their effects?

06:25.430 --> 06:27.360
He was first given a heat-clearing

06:27.360 --> 06:29.290
and exterior-releasing formula,

06:29.630 --> 06:31.480
but it had little effect.

06:31.830 --> 06:33.360
We then tried

06:33.510 --> 06:35.480
a prescription
for nourishing qi and blood.

06:35.480 --> 06:37.480
His Majesty's strength recovered a bit,

06:37.480 --> 06:40.390
but his condition didn't improve at all.

06:40.870 --> 06:42.800
You've explained it in such detail.

06:42.800 --> 06:44.750
It seems you've put a lot of work into it.

06:44.750 --> 06:46.480
You flatter me, Physician Han.

06:46.560 --> 06:47.830
I once had the honor

06:47.830 --> 06:50.830
of serving as an assistant
to the previous Physician Han,

06:50.830 --> 06:51.920
so I would never be negligent

06:51.920 --> 06:53.430
in matters of diagnosis.

06:55.800 --> 06:57.000
You are

06:57.870 --> 06:59.390
Uncle Song?

06:59.680 --> 07:00.070
Yes.

07:01.480 --> 07:02.680
It's been years.

07:02.680 --> 07:04.480
You've grown into a young woman.

07:06.070 --> 07:08.240
I didn't expect that
after all these years,

07:08.240 --> 07:10.430
my father's medical skills
are still recognized.

07:10.430 --> 07:11.920
What happened to the Han family

07:11.920 --> 07:13.380
back then was suspicious.

07:13.480 --> 07:16.430
I believe the truth will come out one day.

07:16.480 --> 07:18.240
Physician Han, your identity—

07:18.240 --> 07:20.680
I will keep it strictly confidential.

07:31.390 --> 07:33.600
Have you remembered everything?

07:37.360 --> 07:38.310
No.

07:46.800 --> 07:49.070
Is there anything unusual
in the medical records?

07:49.070 --> 07:50.680
None.

07:50.950 --> 07:51.870
All treatments

07:51.870 --> 07:53.480
followed standard procedures,

07:53.480 --> 07:54.800
yet His Majesty's condition

07:54.800 --> 07:56.390
has not improved.

07:56.430 --> 07:58.290
That means our approach is wrong.

07:58.950 --> 08:00.870
What caused his coma

08:00.870 --> 08:01.830
is not illness—

08:03.360 --> 08:04.600
but poison.

08:05.040 --> 08:05.680
Poison?

08:06.360 --> 08:07.290
Do you have a way?

08:09.430 --> 08:10.800
I can only try my best.

08:12.630 --> 08:13.430
Xiao Chi.

08:14.070 --> 08:15.390
Can you bring me the list

08:15.390 --> 08:17.000
of tribute gifts from all countries,

08:17.000 --> 08:18.480
along with His Majesty's daily records.

08:18.480 --> 08:19.630
I want to see them.

08:19.750 --> 08:20.560
Tributes?

08:21.630 --> 08:24.230
You think there is a problem
with the tributes?

08:24.480 --> 08:25.720
But these tributes

08:25.720 --> 08:27.750
have always been checked by Zheng.

08:28.480 --> 08:29.870
There can't be any problems.

08:29.870 --> 08:31.680
I know Lord Fei would never do anything

08:31.680 --> 08:33.440
to hurt your brotherly bond.

08:33.789 --> 08:35.669
But even the most careful person

08:35.669 --> 08:37.240
can make mistakes.

08:37.240 --> 08:39.080
I proposed inspecting the tributes

08:39.080 --> 08:41.240
just to clear Lord Fei of suspicion

08:41.480 --> 08:43.360
and to prevent others
from exploiting the situation.

08:43.360 --> 08:45.490
It would be bad if Lord Fei were framed.

08:46.480 --> 08:46.960
Okay.

08:47.600 --> 08:49.260
I'll find someone to get them.

09:02.360 --> 09:04.080
Did you poison Liu Chu?

09:05.630 --> 09:06.630
What do you think?

09:07.440 --> 09:09.000
Was it really Jiang Wanyu?

09:10.630 --> 09:13.080
Jiang Wanyu knew nothing about it.

09:14.630 --> 09:15.760
Then who could it be?

09:17.080 --> 09:20.010
The Hall Master has sent
another spy into the palace?

09:20.360 --> 09:21.220
Are you scared?

09:23.630 --> 09:24.670
Of course I am.

09:25.200 --> 09:26.790
In Caidie Hall,

09:26.870 --> 09:28.530
once a spy is no longer useful,

09:28.670 --> 09:30.080
there is only death.

09:31.840 --> 09:32.970
Where are you going?

09:34.240 --> 09:36.550
I'll go beg the Hall Master
for another chance.

09:36.550 --> 09:37.360
Jin Xi.

09:38.270 --> 09:40.000
Stop aiding and abetting evil.

09:40.480 --> 09:41.630
I have no other choice.

09:41.630 --> 09:42.360
Fei Zheng.

09:42.750 --> 09:43.880
I need the antidote.

09:44.440 --> 09:46.640
But the Hall Master no longer trusts me.

09:47.030 --> 09:48.360
If I don't go and beg her,

09:49.750 --> 09:51.270
I'll be as good as dead.

09:54.200 --> 09:55.730
I can give you the antidote.

10:02.840 --> 10:03.840
You still have it?

10:04.080 --> 10:05.600
I already took that one.

10:06.240 --> 10:07.370
This is another one.

10:07.480 --> 10:09.340
The Hall Master only gave you one.

10:10.550 --> 10:11.790
Just like you said,

10:12.790 --> 10:14.390
as long as I still have value,

10:14.480 --> 10:16.080
asking for another antidote

10:16.270 --> 10:17.270
is not difficult.

10:18.030 --> 10:18.630
Take it.

10:19.150 --> 10:20.210
Aren't you afraid?

10:20.750 --> 10:22.030
Take this,

10:23.360 --> 10:24.690
then go back to Changmo.

10:26.630 --> 10:28.000
I don't want to owe you.

10:28.480 --> 10:29.630
I'll find my own way

10:29.790 --> 10:30.920
to get the antidote.

10:32.390 --> 10:33.200
Jin Xi.

10:43.200 --> 10:44.080
Hall Master.

10:44.240 --> 10:45.870
Liu Chu has been poisoned

10:46.150 --> 10:47.670
and is still unconscious.

10:48.030 --> 10:50.240
He is said to have multiple bruises.

10:51.750 --> 10:52.630
It seems

10:52.630 --> 10:54.690
you're more useful than some others.

10:55.870 --> 10:56.670
Come here.

11:05.440 --> 11:07.390
Thank you, Hall Master.

11:08.150 --> 11:09.480
What do you need me for?

11:09.630 --> 11:11.030
I'll do whatever it takes,

11:11.030 --> 11:12.490
even at the cost of my life.

11:12.870 --> 11:14.800
Liu Chu has already been poisoned.

11:56.870 --> 11:58.790
You've only just recovered.

11:58.790 --> 12:00.360
Go back and rest.

12:00.790 --> 12:01.600
No need.

12:02.440 --> 12:03.770
I'll stay here with you.

12:17.030 --> 12:17.510
Here,

12:17.750 --> 12:18.750
have some hot tea.

14:13.440 --> 14:14.630
My lords,

14:14.750 --> 14:16.790
His Majesty is unwell.

14:16.960 --> 14:18.910
Many court matters will need

14:19.120 --> 14:22.320
your decision and handling, Lord Zhang.

14:25.120 --> 14:25.910
Does anyone

14:26.320 --> 14:29.000
have matters to report?

14:34.910 --> 14:36.770
What Jinglan needs most right now

14:36.840 --> 14:38.150
is stability.

14:38.150 --> 14:40.000
His Majesty has yet to wake.

14:40.120 --> 14:42.000
Forgive my treasonous words—

14:42.120 --> 14:44.720
but if something were to happen…

14:45.120 --> 14:46.870
I mean, just hypothetically…

14:47.200 --> 14:47.860
Lord Zhang.

14:48.320 --> 14:49.630
You are the Chief Grand Secretary.

14:49.630 --> 14:51.910
Some matters cannot be considered lightly,

14:51.910 --> 14:54.240
but they also cannot be ignored.

14:54.630 --> 14:55.510
What do you think?

14:55.510 --> 14:58.030
They risk their lives

14:58.030 --> 14:59.790
and say such things,

14:59.840 --> 15:02.630
they could be considered
loyal ministers of Jinglan.

15:02.630 --> 15:03.440
Lord Li.

15:04.720 --> 15:06.120
What do you mean by this?

15:07.240 --> 15:09.000
Nothing.

15:09.000 --> 15:11.000
Just honest advice.

15:11.000 --> 15:11.720
Lord Fei,

15:12.030 --> 15:13.550
don't be angry.

15:13.550 --> 15:14.390
Indeed.

15:14.510 --> 15:16.030
Could His Majesty's illness

15:16.030 --> 15:17.960
have something to do with Lord Fei?

15:19.790 --> 15:21.720
If you have something to say,

15:22.390 --> 15:23.440
just speak frankly.

15:23.440 --> 15:25.320
In fact, we find

15:25.390 --> 15:27.790
His Majesty's illness rather suspicious.

15:27.790 --> 15:29.910
Ever since you and Xiao Chi

15:29.910 --> 15:31.440
returned from Tianlang Pass,

15:31.440 --> 15:32.630
strange things

15:32.840 --> 15:34.440
have been happening in Jinglan.

15:34.440 --> 15:35.270
Yes.

15:35.670 --> 15:36.390
First the incident in Huangpi Village,

15:36.390 --> 15:38.240
then Xiao Chi,

15:38.240 --> 15:40.120
and now His Majesty.

15:40.120 --> 15:42.630
It's hard not to find this suspicious.

15:42.630 --> 15:43.600
That's right.

15:43.600 --> 15:46.440
I heard that the one treating His Majesty

15:46.600 --> 15:49.600
is the woman who returned
from Changmo with you.

15:50.000 --> 15:50.630
Lord Fei,

15:50.870 --> 15:54.150
that makes you look suspect
of colluding with outsiders.

15:54.320 --> 15:54.750
Everyone.

15:54.750 --> 15:55.750
Alright.

15:56.320 --> 15:57.840
The court

15:57.840 --> 15:59.970
is not a place for you to pass judgment.

16:00.120 --> 16:03.240
His Majesty's condition is still unknown,

16:03.440 --> 16:06.240
yet you're already
suspecting senior ministers.

16:06.390 --> 16:07.990
What kind of conduct is this?

16:08.510 --> 16:09.480
Lord Zhang

16:09.480 --> 16:10.910
is right.

16:11.440 --> 16:14.550
But what you said is also reasonable.

16:15.120 --> 16:16.520
If His Majesty's illness

16:16.550 --> 16:19.360
is truly related to Fei Zheng, Xiao Chi,

16:19.360 --> 16:21.510
and Han Yunling,

16:21.630 --> 16:23.830
then we might as well interrogate them.

16:24.240 --> 16:26.600
Maybe we can find some clues.

16:31.550 --> 16:32.750
How dare you

16:32.910 --> 16:34.510
spread rumors in the court!

16:57.720 --> 16:58.790
Your Highness.

16:59.030 --> 17:01.550
The court ministers
are all in heated debate.

17:01.550 --> 17:02.750
What are they saying?

17:02.840 --> 17:04.030
They say that

17:04.200 --> 17:05.160
if

17:05.160 --> 17:06.790
His Majesty does not wake up…

17:10.109 --> 17:11.310
Just a group of treacherous officials

17:11.310 --> 17:12.369
spreading rumors.

17:13.200 --> 17:13.880
They should

17:14.510 --> 17:15.440
all be executed.

17:15.440 --> 17:18.109
Fortunately,
Lord Zhang stabilized the situation,

17:18.109 --> 17:20.790
with General Xiao and Lord Fei's support.

17:21.349 --> 17:22.640
In times like this,

17:22.790 --> 17:24.310
no one can be trusted.

17:24.790 --> 17:27.750
General Xiao and Lord Fei
hold you in high regard,

17:27.790 --> 17:29.960
and they share a deep brotherly bond
with His Majesty.

17:29.960 --> 17:32.200
They are unlikely to act as you fear.

17:33.830 --> 17:35.640
Everyone grows up,

17:36.550 --> 17:38.240
and people can change.

17:41.030 --> 17:42.790
Have the Xieying Guard get ready.

17:42.790 --> 17:44.400
If anything happens in the palace,

17:44.400 --> 17:45.660
we can respond in time.

17:46.000 --> 17:46.640
Yes.

17:49.920 --> 17:52.240
Some ministers' objections

17:52.240 --> 17:53.790
are not without reason.

17:54.000 --> 17:56.400
If this has nothing to do with you,

17:56.400 --> 17:58.110
then you must find a way

17:58.640 --> 18:00.040
to prove your innocence.

18:00.550 --> 18:02.160
If we cure His Majesty,

18:02.310 --> 18:03.640
that will prove our innocence.

18:03.640 --> 18:04.960
In that case,

18:04.960 --> 18:06.240
I am quite curious.

18:06.240 --> 18:07.400
What kind of illness

18:07.400 --> 18:09.130
is His Majesty suffering from?

18:09.400 --> 18:11.110
It is not an ordinary illness.

18:11.480 --> 18:14.270
It is a rare poison.

18:15.240 --> 18:16.110
Poison?

18:19.440 --> 18:22.790
Since His Majesty has been poisoned
by something so rare,

18:23.240 --> 18:25.000
how can he be cured?

18:25.000 --> 18:26.590
This is no ordinary poison.

18:26.720 --> 18:28.850
It requires an extraordinary remedy.

18:28.960 --> 18:30.440
I have already found a clue,

18:30.440 --> 18:33.310
and discussed it with General Xiao.

18:33.400 --> 18:34.640
Rest assured, my lords.

18:34.640 --> 18:35.790
With me,

18:35.830 --> 18:37.350
the truth will be found

18:37.350 --> 18:39.010
and His Majesty will be cured.

18:45.240 --> 18:46.110
Your Highness.

18:48.590 --> 18:50.320
His Majesty has been poisoned.

18:52.400 --> 18:53.350
Poisoned?

19:07.110 --> 19:08.240
By order of the Eldest Princess,

19:08.240 --> 19:09.440
from today on,

19:09.440 --> 19:11.000
you are confined to the Consort's Palace

19:11.000 --> 19:12.200
and may not leave.

19:13.030 --> 19:13.590
Lan.

19:13.590 --> 19:14.790
Why am I confined?

19:15.200 --> 19:16.550
His Majesty is unconscious.

19:16.550 --> 19:20.080
All related persons are to be confined
pending investigation.

19:23.440 --> 19:24.590
Lan!

19:25.030 --> 19:26.240
Lan.

19:26.400 --> 19:27.110
Lan!

19:27.110 --> 19:28.640
Take me to see Her Highness.

19:28.640 --> 19:30.240
Lan!

19:30.640 --> 19:32.110
Lan!

19:32.350 --> 19:34.830
I want to see Her Highness.

19:34.830 --> 19:37.440
What exactly happened to His Majesty?

19:38.550 --> 19:40.640
I want to see him.

19:40.920 --> 19:42.350
Lan.

20:10.720 --> 20:12.240
It's getting late.

20:12.400 --> 20:13.400
Go back and rest.

20:13.790 --> 20:15.190
I will stay here tonight.

20:15.590 --> 20:17.110
You were on watch yesterday.

20:17.110 --> 20:18.790
Let me do it today.

20:20.240 --> 20:21.310
Then why not

20:21.750 --> 20:22.400
both of us

20:23.440 --> 20:24.200
stay?

20:25.830 --> 20:27.110
I'm sure Chu

20:27.480 --> 20:28.610
would agree as well.

20:33.590 --> 20:34.310
Why

20:34.960 --> 20:35.960
don't we

20:36.440 --> 20:37.640
have a drink with him?

20:38.790 --> 20:39.550
Guards!

20:39.880 --> 20:40.440
Yes.

20:40.920 --> 20:41.780
Bring the wine.

20:48.000 --> 20:48.790
Please.

21:04.030 --> 21:04.750
Chu.

21:05.350 --> 21:06.720
Look, Xiao Chi has already

21:06.720 --> 21:07.960
poured you a drink.

21:07.960 --> 21:09.160
Get well soon.

21:09.310 --> 21:11.160
And get up and drink it.

21:11.440 --> 21:12.000
Come on,

21:12.310 --> 21:13.440
today the three of us

21:13.790 --> 21:15.190
will drink until we drop.

21:16.790 --> 21:17.920
Drink until we drop.

21:24.440 --> 21:27.030
We grew up together

21:28.920 --> 21:29.720
and

21:30.110 --> 21:31.770
went through many hardships.

21:32.030 --> 21:33.350
Our brotherhood

21:33.640 --> 21:35.030
is what I value most.

21:36.440 --> 21:37.310
This cup

21:38.790 --> 21:40.110
is for you two.

21:42.790 --> 21:43.640
Please.

21:52.550 --> 21:53.790
You two may leave.

21:53.790 --> 21:54.270
Yes.

21:57.200 --> 21:58.270
Lord Li,

21:58.480 --> 21:59.790
what do you mean?

21:59.790 --> 22:00.680
Lord Zhang,

22:00.680 --> 22:02.310
I've come to pay my respects.

22:02.920 --> 22:03.720
Look—

22:03.750 --> 22:06.160
these are rare
surviving copies of ancient books

22:06.160 --> 22:07.400
from across the country
and various dynasties

22:07.400 --> 22:10.240
that I've collected for you.

22:11.400 --> 22:12.960
Such good books

22:13.000 --> 22:15.510
should be given to
those who appreciate them.

22:15.510 --> 22:18.110
Keeping them at my place
would be a waste,

22:18.240 --> 22:19.880
so I've brought them to you.

22:23.000 --> 22:24.000
Lord Li.

22:24.750 --> 22:27.160
His Majesty is still unconscious.

22:27.590 --> 22:30.350
How can I be in the mood to read?

22:31.110 --> 22:32.160
Right.

22:33.240 --> 22:34.000
That...

22:34.310 --> 22:35.350
that is another important reason

22:35.350 --> 22:37.030
why I am here.

22:38.960 --> 22:42.440
If His Majesty were truly…

22:45.440 --> 22:46.680
I mean,

22:46.680 --> 22:48.110
of course he is blessed

22:48.110 --> 22:49.350
and will be fine.

22:49.830 --> 22:51.510
But some things

22:51.510 --> 22:53.510
must be considered in advance.

22:55.350 --> 22:56.680
I also hope

22:57.000 --> 22:59.720
to find answers in these books.

22:59.720 --> 23:01.550
Lord Zhang.

23:02.000 --> 23:03.160
I've arranged

23:03.160 --> 23:04.920
these ancient books

23:04.920 --> 23:06.590
for you by dynasty.

23:06.590 --> 23:07.590
You can go through them carefully

23:07.590 --> 23:09.790
when you have time.

23:10.440 --> 23:11.590
In fact,

23:11.720 --> 23:12.480
I believe

23:12.790 --> 23:13.650
you've already

23:13.960 --> 23:16.510
understood many things in your heart.

23:18.030 --> 23:19.240
Yes.

23:21.030 --> 23:22.590
If His Majesty

23:23.030 --> 23:24.920
never wakes up,

23:25.920 --> 23:28.310
once Consort Ling gives birth,

23:28.310 --> 23:31.370
I will support
the only remaining heir of the Liu family

23:31.550 --> 23:34.440
to keep Jinglan prosperous.

23:35.590 --> 23:37.000
That may be so,

23:37.030 --> 23:38.920
but we don't even know

23:38.920 --> 23:40.920
whether the child is a boy or a girl.

23:41.310 --> 23:42.790
And even if it is a boy,

23:43.160 --> 23:44.640
whether he can survive

23:44.830 --> 23:46.790
is still uncertain.

23:50.240 --> 23:51.830
So what do you mean?

23:53.750 --> 23:55.310
I mean,

23:56.200 --> 23:57.790
The Liu family and Jinglan

23:58.440 --> 24:00.200
are two different things.

24:01.720 --> 24:03.550
I know you are loyal

24:03.550 --> 24:05.640
to the late Emperor and the Liu family.

24:05.640 --> 24:06.270
But

24:06.790 --> 24:08.790
if the Liu bloodline truly dies out,

24:10.200 --> 24:11.510
what will happen to Jinglan?

24:11.510 --> 24:13.030
To the people?

24:13.160 --> 24:15.110
And to the court?

24:20.350 --> 24:22.240
This is too tricky.

24:23.510 --> 24:25.480
So what do you

24:26.110 --> 24:27.200
really mean?

24:36.350 --> 24:38.240
My real meaning is…

24:40.790 --> 24:41.720
Lord Zhang.

24:42.110 --> 24:44.400
You are the head of the ministers.

24:45.310 --> 24:49.400
If the Liu bloodline truly dies out,

24:49.550 --> 24:50.750
wouldn't this empire

24:51.240 --> 24:53.000
be yours?

24:53.750 --> 24:54.310
You...

24:54.960 --> 24:58.160
How dare you say such treasonous words!

24:59.640 --> 25:00.590
Right.

25:01.720 --> 25:03.790
We are both assistant ministers.

25:03.920 --> 25:05.720
You've always been thoughtful.

25:05.880 --> 25:07.270
It's only right for you

25:08.000 --> 25:09.350
to think ahead.

25:09.350 --> 25:11.080
I'm just doing this for Jinglan

25:11.640 --> 25:13.400
and for the people.

25:19.350 --> 25:20.160
Lord Li.

25:21.030 --> 25:21.590
Lord Li,

25:21.920 --> 25:22.960
what's wrong?

25:23.640 --> 25:24.790
Don't panic, Lord Zhang.

25:24.790 --> 25:25.480
Lord Li.

25:25.480 --> 25:26.310
I'm fine.

25:26.400 --> 25:29.790
It's probably just that
His Majesty's poor health

25:29.920 --> 25:32.400
has been keeping me restless,

25:32.640 --> 25:35.200
and this chest pain
may have flared up again.

25:35.920 --> 25:36.830
Then

25:36.830 --> 25:38.400
hurry back to your residence and rest.

25:38.400 --> 25:41.400
We still have to go to the palace
to see His Majesty tomorrow.

25:41.400 --> 25:42.440
Okay.

25:42.440 --> 25:43.510
Take care.

25:44.550 --> 25:45.400
Just go.

25:45.400 --> 25:46.310
Sorry.

25:46.590 --> 25:48.240
I will take my leave now.

25:51.270 --> 25:52.240
Look.

25:55.070 --> 25:56.030
Lord Li.

25:56.400 --> 25:57.440
Your books.

26:00.510 --> 26:03.200
These are not gold or silver,

26:03.200 --> 26:05.640
merely courtesies among gentlemen.

26:05.640 --> 26:08.550
They won't ruin
your reputation, Lord Zhang.

26:08.550 --> 26:09.200
Don't worry.

26:09.200 --> 26:10.240
All right.

26:11.240 --> 26:12.900
Then I'll accept them for now.

26:13.240 --> 26:14.830
I'll read them

26:14.830 --> 26:16.400
after His Majesty awakens.

26:18.310 --> 26:19.640
I shall take my leave.

26:20.240 --> 26:21.200
Take care.

26:47.640 --> 26:48.550
Chu.

26:48.830 --> 26:50.550
Get up and look at Xiao Chi.

26:50.720 --> 26:52.030
He seems troubled.

26:52.750 --> 26:53.640
General Xiao,

26:53.920 --> 26:56.510
why don't you tell your thoughts

26:56.510 --> 26:57.720
to Chu?

26:57.830 --> 26:59.630
He is now the ruler of the nation.

26:59.640 --> 27:00.830
Whatever you want,

27:01.200 --> 27:02.310
he can fulfill it.

27:05.790 --> 27:07.190
I was just thinking about

27:08.350 --> 27:10.410
the three of us when we were children.

27:10.550 --> 27:11.750
Back then,

27:12.200 --> 27:13.460
Chu led us everywhere,

27:14.110 --> 27:15.640
and we were completely carefree.

27:15.640 --> 27:16.900
It was such a good time.

27:32.240 --> 27:33.160
Chu.

27:33.440 --> 27:34.830
Get up and take a look.

27:35.160 --> 27:36.480
Our dear Zheng

27:36.750 --> 27:38.030
is troubled too.

27:40.400 --> 27:42.330
You've married the woman you love,

27:42.720 --> 27:43.640
and I'm just

27:48.790 --> 27:49.720
waiting for you

27:49.720 --> 27:50.830
to wake up

27:51.070 --> 27:53.310
and arrange a marriage for our Lord Fei.

28:01.720 --> 28:02.510
I don't need

28:02.960 --> 28:04.290
any arranged marriage.

28:07.110 --> 28:08.510
In my life,

28:08.750 --> 28:09.830
with you,

28:10.830 --> 28:12.720
and Liu Chu as my brothers,

28:15.400 --> 28:16.640
that is enough.

28:21.350 --> 28:22.610
I ask for nothing more.

28:25.680 --> 28:26.140
Please.

28:36.200 --> 28:37.000
What's wrong?

28:38.640 --> 28:39.440
Nothing.

28:45.400 --> 28:46.730
You're coughing blood,

28:46.830 --> 28:48.230
and you say it's nothing?

28:49.030 --> 28:50.030
It's an old issue.

28:50.640 --> 28:52.640
Ever since I was poisoned last time,

28:54.030 --> 28:55.310
it's been acting up.

28:55.550 --> 28:56.350
I just

28:57.110 --> 28:58.710
have occasional flare-ups.

29:00.440 --> 29:01.510
Wait here for me.

29:01.960 --> 29:03.640
I'll go get Physician Han to check on you.

29:03.640 --> 29:04.440
Zheng.

29:04.920 --> 29:06.400
Don't tell Han Yunling.

29:07.110 --> 29:08.510
I don't want her to worry.

29:09.030 --> 29:09.750
Besides,

29:10.750 --> 29:12.110
she has to find a way

29:12.590 --> 29:13.640
to treat Chu.

29:18.790 --> 29:19.750
Look at you.

29:20.200 --> 29:20.920
I'm fine.

29:21.830 --> 29:22.550
I won't die.

29:23.640 --> 29:24.160
Come on.

29:24.480 --> 29:25.310
Today,

29:25.590 --> 29:26.830
let's drink until we drop.

29:26.830 --> 29:27.720
We'll deal with

29:29.240 --> 29:30.770
everything else tomorrow.

29:36.030 --> 29:36.790
Fine.

29:39.400 --> 29:40.510
You're in this condition

29:40.510 --> 29:41.840
and still want to drink?

29:42.350 --> 29:44.030
You really have a death wish.

29:46.400 --> 29:48.160
We'll talk about everything else

29:48.160 --> 29:49.160
tomorrow.

29:49.640 --> 29:50.720
Okay.
